episodes.title: Julia Fox’s TV Show, Cult Documentaries & Nepo Baby Debate
episodes.description:
On today’s team podcast Sherri Andrew is joined by Harriet Russell & Nana Acheampong to chat new beauty and fashion launches, Julia Fox’s TV show & North West’s performance at the Hollywood Bowl. Plus, they answer your questions on summer occasion wear, the ankle versus long sock debate & the Notting Hill spots to visit.
